pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: The data displayed on this dashboard is collected directly from survey responses and does not come from official country statistics or data sets. It represents the opinions expressed by the young people at the time of the survey, and any conclusions drawn from these responses are the responsibility of the user, not PMNCH. PMNCH is committed to respecting, promoting and protecting the rights and well-being of all individuals. Any views expressed in the survey responses or published materials emerging from this dashboard that contradict this commitment are not endorsed by PMNCH.
